The paper discusses the use of blockchain technology in healthcare, which involves security and privacy concerns (cs.CR), healthcare applications (cs.HC), software engineering practices (cs.SE), data management (cs.DB), and distributed computing (cs.DC). Therefore, the most likely categories are cs.CR and cs.HC, followed by cs.SE, cs.DB, and cs.DC.
